descript.abstract: 10 X 10 Degree Graticule (layer) is a symbolized and labeled display presentation of the World latitude and longitude grids data set. The geographic and attribute data World latitude and longitude grids are symbolized and labeled to create the layer. All features are symbolized as a single symbol. Features are labeled based on the VALUE attribute.
